= SDL_IntersectRect =
Use this function to calculate the intersection of two rectangles.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_bool SDL_IntersectRect(const SDL_Rect* A,
                           const SDL_Rect* B,
                           SDL_Rect*       result)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''A'''
|the first [[SDL_Rect]]
|-
|'''B'''
|the second [[SDL_Rect]]
|-
|'''result'''
|a pointer to an [[SDL_Rect]] that is filled with the intersection of rectangles '''A''' and '''B'''
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns SDL_TRUE if there is an intersection, SDL_FALSE otherwise.

